A lot of people don't know our work.
Dactyloscopy is an exact science, without the possibility of error, which can play a key role in the decision-making of crimes.
In addition to identifying the corpses, these people help in researching crimes such as theft or murder and confirm the identity of the captured persons.
When they get caught, a lot of delinquents present fake IDs or have no papers at all.
We'll take their fingerprints and search their database.
The investigator said that in the event of injuries, he had to remove a piece of the house wall, because in this place the thief leaned on to pull out a safe full of jewelry and money.
